  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a bowl, mix together the masarepa, egg, feta cheese, parsley, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Heat a non-stick pan with 1 tablespoon of vegetable oil over medium heat.",
    "Shape the masarepa mixture into a ball and flatten it slightly into a disk shape.",
    "Cook the masarepa disk in the pan for 2-3 minutes on each side, until crispy and golden brown.",
    "Transfer the pan to the preheated oven and bake for 5-7 minutes, until the masarepa is crispy and cooked through.",
    "Wrap the crispy masarepa in a ssam-wrap and serve hot."
  ],
